itiated after the Saville Inquiry found that none of the victims was posing a threat to soldiers when they were shot. </p> <p>Following the publication of the Saville report in 2010, prime minister David Cameron apologised for the Army’s actions, branding them “unjustified and unjustifiable”. </p> <p>In September, the PSNI announced their intention to interview seven former soldiers about their involvement on the day. <br /></p>","internalOctopusCode":"10972868","productionOffice":"UK","newspaperEditionDate":"2015-11-12T00:00:00Z","hasStoryPackage":"false","internalPageCode":"2405645","internalRevision":"191","internalContentCode":"458371672","publication":"The Guardian","trailText":"Ex-paratrooper, 66, arrested on suspicion of murdering three civil rights demonstrators in 1972 is out on bail, police said","allowUgc":"false","headline":"Former British soldier held over Bloody Sunday killings released on bail","byline":"Press Association","isInappropriateForSponsorship":"false","commentable":"false","firstPublicationDate":"2015-11-11T22:00:15Z","thumbnail":"http://media.guim.co.uk/105826d882d790da7e77bd824e5168b2197a659c/0_316_2564_1539/140.jpg","isPremoderated":"false","internalComposerCode":"5643b5c5e4b05f01ec0a2df7","newspaperPageNumber":"20","standfirst":"<p>Ex-paratrooper, 66, arrested on suspicion of murdering three civil rights demonstrators in 1972 is out on bail, police said</p>","creationDate":"2015-11-11T21:40:21Z","showInRelatedContent":"true","lastModified":"2015-11-12T00:15:03.110Z","legallySensitive":"false"},"webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2015/nov/11/former-british-soldier-held-over-bloody-sunday-killings-released-on-bail","apiUrl":"http://content.guardianapis.com/uk-news/2015/nov/11/former-british-soldier-held-over-bloody-sunday-killings-released-on-bail","sectionName":"UK news","elements":[{"id":"105826d882d790da7e77bd824e5168b2197a659c","relation":"main","type":"image","assets":[{"type":"image","file":"http://media.guim.co.uk/105826d8